    "sections": {
        "description": "<p>This plugin adds another comment functionality in post/edit screen.<br />\nYou can communicate with your editorial/admin team members within your WordPress screen.<br />\nIn the setting page, You can enable/disable the function for each post type.</p>\n<h4>UPDATE in version 2</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Display comment list on the post list screen as well.</li>\n<li>Show revision and status change in comment timeline.</li>\n</ul>\n",
        "installation": "<ol>\n<li>Upload the plugin package to the plugins directory.</li>\n<li>Activate the plugin through the Plugins menu in WordPress.</li>\n</ol>\n",
        "changelog": "<h4>2.0.1</h4>\n<p>A minor bug fix.</p>\n<h4>2.0.0</h4>\n<p>Add revision &amp; changed status in comment timeline with filtering function.<br />\nAdd display a comment in the list screen of each post type.<br />\nTested up to 5.5.1.</p>\n<h4>1.2.0</h4>\n<p>Fix deactivation action. Thanks to Jevgenijs Cernihovics.<br />\nAdd Uninstallation action.<br />\nSupport multisite.</p>\n<h4>1.1.0</h4>\n<p>Add option page. &amp; Tested up to 5.2.1.</p>\n<h4>1.0.1</h4>\n<p>Add translation file &amp; Tested up to 5.0.3.</p>\n<h4>1.0.0</h4>\n<p>first version.</p>\n"
    },
